education.institution: International institute of Information Technology IIIT pune

profile.summary: A passionate Full Stack Developer with expertise in frontend, backend, and DevOps technologies. I excel in creating seamless and dynamic web applications. Transform your vision into stunning digital reality with expert development services tailored to your unique business needs.

projects.name: Todo Application
projects.description: Developing a to-do app with Node.js, MongoDB, Express, and React involves creating a backend with Node.js and Express for API endpoints, using MongoDB for database storage, and building a frontend with React for a responsive user interface. Integrating these technologies allows for a full-stack application capable of managing tasks efficiently.

projects.name: Dukkan Web Interface
projects.description: Developed Dukkan interface using Tailwind CSS, optimizing Ul for enhanced user experience. Implemented responsive design principles to ensure compatibility across devices. Enhanced frontend functionality for improved usability and performance.
